{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"14051-the-best-thing-ever","title":"The Best Thing Ever","description":"Muzi loves to build with his toys. But when he leaves them behind to travel to uGogo’s house, he discovers something very special about the world. And he learns something new about himself.\r\n\r\n","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Melissa  Fagan ","Stefania Origgi"],"illustrators":["Lauren   Nel"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Book Dash","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/14051-the-best-thing-ever"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/118153/size3/bc2ba70b6ef08fef7c20b01264e48156.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/118153/size6/bc2ba70b6ef08fef7c20b01264e48156.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39278/size6/06e9409400fac670fbbd691f76d69b71.jpg","text":"Muzi loves to\nbuild things. He dreams of building the best thing ever.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39279/size6/38e961b1806c44c52fa6fef8864c36d4.jpg","text":"Once, he built a\nshelter for his toys.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39280/size6/b895149031e129024a6b8ee430a58401.jpg","text":"But it wasn’t the\nbest thing ever.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39281/size6/8e9f79ad65a4fb1b96cefb630e03a4ba.jpg","text":"Yesterday he\nbuilt a bridge for his animals.\n \nIt was a good\nthing.\nBut not the best…","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39282/size6/95ff1eecb3eaffdc6ce8f994f6f546db.jpg","text":"Today Muzi is\ngoing to visit uGogo.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39283/size6/51dd626a86dbb108b28bf62eb59eb8e7.jpg","text":"He is sad. \nWithout his toys, how can he build \nthe best thing ever?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39284/size6/8364c72a85b0044c10931e98e4679fa8.jpg","text":"At the bus stop,\nMuzi is amazed.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39285/size6/053023005925be9ca966b4de35718809.jpg","text":"He sees red things and blue things.\nSmall things and big things.\nNew things and old things.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39286/size6/f5baf8aca8274c7afc8224abd8e0be42.jpg","text":"Muzi has a new\nidea for building the best thing ever.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39287/size6/a0d9d51abe2805a6931154d4cbb6a3cc.jpg","text":"On the road to\nuGogo’s,\nMuzi finds many\nthings.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39288/size6/454fb29b7924ce8bef6f3234ca4aa66e.jpg","text":"Long things and\nshort things.\nRound things and\nsquare things.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39289/size6/eb04ffb9b1d338fe2ec7750eb45bf92e.jpg","text":"By the riverside, \nMuzi finds more\nthings.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39290/size6/5aa0a7471a8e54d0f6bf9beea5e8019d.jpg","text":"Soft things and\npointy things.\nGreen things and\nbrown things.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39291/size6/c0926d7a5b0aeb945f135c78eb2f47dc.jpg","text":"\"Look, Muzi! \nWe\nare here.\"","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39292/size6/35444f4802164659dcd2c6de89d4671f.jpg","text":"While uGogo bakes\nfor\nthe hungry\ntravellers…","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39293/size6/73d3b70d828432e790fe3e7c0e6e5ccf.jpg","text":"Muzi builds.","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39294/size6/53f304b1d0371ae329ac46d8d4373285.jpg","text":"Look uGogo, a new\nhouse for you.\nOh, Muzi, laughs uGogo.\nThis is the best thing ever!","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39295/size6/821c5bd5abd5cbc08be12434f1f9357b.jpg","text":"uGogo, uGogo! says\nMuzi.\nThe world is full\nof toys.\nLook what I can\nbuild.","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/39296/size6/5c5a30f62441b179c547b38d1b9edd09.jpg","text":"20/20","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":19,"words":184}}